#: src/uagent/util_tools.py:2137
msgid ""
"The bullet points listed below are excerpts from this user's long-term memory (persistent memos). Use them as background information about the user. However, always prioritize newly provided information in the conversation, and if it contradicts older information, adopt the latest information.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Vipengele vya orodha vilivyo hapa chini ni dondoo kutoka kumbukumbu ya muda mrefu ya mtumiaji huyu (memo za kudumu). Vitumie kama taarifa ya msingi kuhusu mtumiaji. Hata hivyo, daima zingatia taarifa mpya zilizotolewa katika mazungumzo, na ikiwa zinapingana na taarifa za zamani, chukua taarifa ya hivi karibuni.\n"
"\n"

